Hi Aneesha â€“ I would try this:

Add 'flex-wrap: wrap' (allows items to wrap) and 'gap' property (adds space between items) to .container and remove column rules (best to not mix flexbox and columns).

```.container{
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 16px;
}```
Then set the width of the items explicitly at different breakpoints:

Mobile (no media query)

```.item {
width: 50%; 
}```
900px
```@media (min-width: 900px) {
 .item  { width: 33.3333333% }
}```
